Wrapper typed delle Tauri commands:

```typescript
getDesktopBackendInfo(): Promise<BackendInfo>
getRole(): Promise<'admin' | 'sala' | null>
setRole(role): Promise<{restart_required: boolean}>
discoverLanPcs(roleFilter, timeoutMs): Promise<LanPc[]>
